1：下载SDK的JAR包
https://developers.dingtalk.com/document/resourcedownload/download-server-sdk/title-12y-g4g-zn2?pnamespace=tutorial


2：导入Maven
mvn install:install-file -DgroupId=com.dingtalk.api -DartifactId=top-api-sdk-dev -Dversion=ding-open-mc-SNAPSHOT -Dfile=taobao-sdk-java-auto_1479188381469-20210512.jar -Dpackaging=jar -DgeneratePom=true


3：配置POM
<!--钉钉工具包-->
<dependency>
    <groupId>com.dingtalk.api</groupId>
    <artifactId>top-api-sdk-dev</artifactId>
    <version>ding-open-mc-SNAPSHOT</version>
</dependency>